<plot>Murphy is the sole survivor of his crew, that has been massacred by a German U-Boat in the closing days of World War II. He lands on a forgotten island and begins to plot his vengeance. He wishes to sink the U-Boat that has floated up by means of any method imaginable to him, and sets about to make the courageous attempt, assisted by Louie, the islands Government Administrator.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?382113</url></doc>
